lyrics:
[Verse]
Pepa's got a stylish jacket, oh so cool
He struts down the street like nobody's fool
But his buddy's braying, "Give it back, Pepa, it's mine
But Pepa's not budging, he's gonna draw the line

[Chorus]
Pepa wants to keep his jacket, wear it with pride
He won't give it up, no matter how hard they try
He's the king of swing, rockin' through the night
Pepa's gonna keep his jacket, that's his delight
